Package net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.layout Description

Use of layout API is deprecated. Control should be given to web designers / developers over the layout and presentation of the data output by MIWT.

See the swing api for usage examples. http://java.sun.com/docs/books/tutorial/uiswing/layout/gridbag.html http://java.sun.com/docs/books/tutorial/uiswing/layout/gridbagConstraints.html http://java.sun.com/docs/books/tutorial/uiswing/layout/gridbagExample.html
